column5: I am looking for an 520 x 10 tire for my small boat trailer any body now where i can find one used thanks...
You sure about that size?  I've looked and haven't found a hit anywhere. I found that size was used on Austin Minis, way back, converted to 145R10 metric, now 165R10, good luck.
You sure it's not a 5.30-12 Kelv
yes I know its of a mini.. that has the wheels for it on the trailer.. the spare is the one I need it for.. all cracked up..
no it is a 520x10 for sure Wayne
I even took the hub and tried to see if *I could get it to fit an 8inch and no go..
Okay.. just checkin as I have at least one of those here somewhere.
Best she can.. in Florida with Leah 'till tomorrow night visting Leah's father.
Great news Wayne hope it stays that way for sure
